{"tid":674383,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(回歸免簽) AC米蘭有意費蘭尼！","createTime":"2018-05-22T15:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T00:52:01.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa4a89890964a03b673ef99b34dcd9f4d0c48002","tid":674383,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"　　AC米蘭今年夏天進入了歐霸盃正賽，而在中場方面紅黑軍團希望引進曼聯中場費蘭尼。後者的合約將在今年夏天到期。<br />\n<br />\n　　在下個月，費蘭尼與曼聯的合約就將到期，他將成為一名自由球員。《每日郵報》消息表示，AC米蘭的體育總監已經在週日採取了行動，他希望比利時中場可以在下季加入AC米蘭。消息中指出，AC米蘭為費蘭尼提供了300萬歐元的年薪，簽約三年。費蘭尼目前的週薪為12萬英鎊。稅後大約在350萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n　　米拉比利：「費蘭尼？他可能是一名重要的球員。事實上，他很出色。我們知道他不會和曼聯續約，但是想要簽下他仍然很睏難。我們會去做出一些努力，但是在我們宣佈一名球員之前，首先要完成他的交易。」<br />\n<br />\n　　費蘭尼2013年以2750英鎊的價格從愛華頓加盟紅魔曼聯。不過今季他在摩連奴手下失去了位置，出場16次僅僅5次正選，貢獻4粒入球。"},{"pid":"1e554bce632da507a89e6bec339ee19cba1b9d99","tid":674383,"uid":31314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.calcionews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/milan-wearesorich.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.calcionews24.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fmilan-wearesorich.jpg&h=32dd8f17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96433f3161b1942c6ad1565ba0c9f5adfecee82c","tid":674383,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e554bce632da507a89e6bec339ee19cba1b9d99","tid":674383,"uid":31314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.calcionews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/milan-wearesorich.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.calcionews24.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fmilan-wearesorich.jpg&h=32dd8f17&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p